    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1865-04-22T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1865-04-22T00:00:00-05:00" n="461"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d461">
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. de Geofroy</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Hunter</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of France to the United States</hi>, <hi
                                rend="italic">Washington</hi>,</placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1865-04-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">April</hi> 22, 1865.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> The French community at New York held on Tuesday,
                    the 18th of this month, a meeting under the presidency of the consul general of
                    his Majesty in that city, where a series of resolutions was adopted, of which
                    three copies have been sent to me; one for the government of the United States,
                    another for the family of the deceased President Lincoln, and a third for that
                    of Mr. Seward.</p>
                <p>These resolutions express the indignation and the sorrow which the horrible
                    outrages of the last week have caused our countrymen to experience.</p>
                <p>I pray you, sir, to be so good as to cause these papers to reach their
                    destination, and I seize this occasion to renew to you the assurances of my most
                    distinguished consideration.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>L. DE GEOFBOY.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">William Hunter</hi>, <hi rend="italic">&amp;c.,
                            &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi>
                    </p>
                    <p>[For enclosures see Appendix, separate volume.]</p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
